--[[
STRUCTURE

{InternalItemName (string), size (int), pathToPictureFile (string), pictureSizeX (int), pictureSizeY (int), ItemType (string), Description (string), TranslationOfItem (string), [itemAction (string)]},
InternalItemName: The name of the item that will be used by the gamemode (must be in english!)
size: Can be any value, see itemWeightTable at the end to change how many slots the item should occupy/take
pathToPictureFile: Only the last part of the filepath (example: 'item.png')
pictureSizeX: The size of the picture in length (x)
pictureSizeY: The size of the picture in width (y)
ItemType: Type of item
Description: Use \n after ~34 characters (spaces included!) to begin new file, else the sentence will but cut off
TranslationOfItem: Name of the item as it should appear in the inventory
itemAction: Optional, determines what should happen when you rightclick the item (TO TRANSLATORS: Don't translate this string!)

]]


